ContainedObjects.Name: Notecard
ContainedObjects.Description:
Death Knights have only three Runes: one Blood, one Frost, and one Unholy.
They regain Runes at the end of each combat round and during a Rest action.
They start and end each combat with 0 Energy.
Once applied, Diseases and their effects remain active until any opponent is defeated, or combat ends.
